<opener><salute>Viro <choice><abbr>Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>clariss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>clarissimo</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Celeberr.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Celeberrimo</expan></choice>
<lb/>D. Johanni <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> Petrus <choice><abbr>Ant.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Antonius</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelotti</rs></salute></opener>
<p>Nisi spes esset de proximo reditu <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agna<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>ti</rs> Tui quem propediem expectamus, dubitarem
                <lb/>Litteras binas<note type="editorial">Meint zwei Briefe: Den Brief vom <rs key="B_1717-09-03_991170515153505501" type="letter">3.09.1717</rs> und den Brief vom<rs key="B_1717-09-09_991170515153405501" type="letter">9.09.1717</rs>.</note> (quas diversis temporibus pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terito
                <lb/>mense ad Te dedi) evanuisse. Hanc tertiam
                <lb/>mitto Tibi epistolam<!-- Gemeint ist vorliegender Brief selbst --> Vir <choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissime</expan></choice> ut certior fiam
                <lb/>num antecedentes meas<note type="editorial">Meint wie oben zwei Briefe: Den Brief vom <rs key="B_1717-09-03_991170515153505501" type="letter">3.09.1717</rs> und den Brief vom<rs key="B_1717-09-09_991170515153405501" type="letter">9.09.1717</rs>.</note> acceperis nec ne. Si acce<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>pisti spero <choice><abbr>humaniss.<hi rend="sup">am</hi></abbr><expan>humanissimam</expan></choice> <rs key="B_1717-12-01_991170515152805501" type="letter">responsionem</rs><note type="editorial">Die Antwort von Joh. I B. datiert vom 1.12.1717, erwähnt aber nicht, ob Nic. I B. den Brief spedierte oder ob er einen anderen Weg nahm.</note>, quam fortasse
                <lb/>afferet <choice><abbr>Doctiss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Doctissimus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nepos</rs> Tuus. Uni mearum litterarum<!-- Meint den vorliegenden Brief. Systemnummer für brieftag eingefügt. -->
<lb/>adjeci <rs key="brieftag" type="letter">epistolam</rs><note type="editorial">Der Brief scheint nicht erhalten zu sein.</note> pro <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filio</rs> Tuo <choice><abbr>ingeniosiss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>ingeniosissimo</expan></choice>, quem
                <lb/>scivi scripsisse bis<rs key="brieftag" type="letter"/><note type="editorial">Die Briefe scheinen nicht erhalten zu sein.</note> <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Parisiis</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavium</rs> ad Nobilem
                <lb/>Monach<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Ciceran<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice><!-- persontag --><note type="editorial">Benediktinermönch aus Zizers (Graubünden)?</note> <choice><abbr>S.</abbr><expan>Sancti</expan></choice> Benedicti, qui in hanc
                <lb/>civitatem<!-- orttag --> heri vespere se contulit. Obstupesco
                <lb/>quod <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filius</rs> ornatissimus nullam ad me miserit
                <lb/>epistolam<choice><orig>.</orig><reg>,</reg></choice> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipue quia ipsum rogavi ut fre<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>quenter ad me scriberet et quia nullam, uti
                <lb/>opinor, occasionem habet ut mei obliviscatur.
                <lb/>Si h<choice><orig><g ref="#ihat">î</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice>c esset in pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentiar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, <choice><abbr>D.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Dominus</expan></choice> Robertus Brown<!-- persontag -->
<lb/>Anglus plurimis beneficiis ipsum <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Fili<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
                <lb/>cumularet. Requirit enim Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ceptorem pro
                <lb/>Mathesi addiscenda<choice><orig>.</orig><reg>;</reg></choice> nimis celeriter discessit
                <pb facs="1078959" n="2"/>
<lb/><rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs>; ubi si redire volet a me diligetur
                <lb/>atque occasione data promovebitur. Alia vice
                <lb/>ad Eum scribo. Rogo igitur Vir Amicissime
                <lb/>ut ipsi hanc epistolam<!-- Vorliegender Brief 000056680. brieftag durch Systemnummer ersetzt. --> amandes, moneasque
                <lb/>me magna expectatione suas litteras concu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>piscere. De rebus Litterariis nihil ad Te
                <lb/>scribo quia satis superque fortassis de his rebus
                <lb/>in pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cedentibus meis litteris<note type="editorial">Siehe zum Beispiel Michelottis Briefe vom <rs key="B_1717-09-03_991170515153505501" type="letter">03. September</rs> und vom <rs key="B_1717-09-09_991170515153405501" type="letter">09. September 1717</rs>, in denen er verschiedene physiologische Fragestellungen anspricht.</note> scripsi. Non in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>venio apud me <choice><abbr>ingeniosiss.<hi rend="sup">m</hi></abbr><expan>ingeniosissimam</expan></choice> et valde raram
                <lb/>dissertationem tuam <rs key="biblio_WIW87HR7" type="biblio">de Nutritione</rs>. Credo
                <lb/>quod <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filius</rs> Tuus mihi carissimus eam secum
                <lb/>transtulerit. Si possibile esset alia vice
                <lb/>ipsum viderem libentissime quare si habes
                <lb/>mitte per <rs key="place_VER-tirola" type="place">Tyrolim</rs> nullo habito ad expensas
                <lb/>respectu, ego enim omnia<!-- Entity fehlt noch: &omnia; --> persolvam. Si alias
                <lb/>habes dissertationes rogo ut communices; uti
                <lb/>etiam si quid novisti publici iuris fact<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
                <lb/>istuc, <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Parisiis</rs> aut alibi, mihi impertias peto sive
                <lb/>spectet ad res mathematicas, sive ad philo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>sophicas, sive ad medicas. Libenter etiam
                <lb/>a Te scirem titulos omnium<!-- Entity fehlt noch: &omnium; --> operum a <choice><abbr>Cele<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>berr.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Celeberrimo</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118571249" type="person">Leibnitio</rs> compositor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, et an acceperis
                <pb facs="1078960" n="3"/>
<lb/>libr<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-11757645X" type="person">Gulielmini</rs> <rs key="biblio_CZST2I45" type="biblio">de Natura Fluminum</rs>,
                <lb/>quem ante ann<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> misi.</p> <closer><salute>Vale Vir <choice><abbr>Doctiss.<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr><expan>Doctissime</expan></choice> scias<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>que mihi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipue tuam iucundissimam amiciti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
                    <lb/>semper futuram fore carissim<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice></salute>.</closer>
